## Database Schema

```sql
CREATE TABLE chat_sessions (
    id          TEXT PRIMARY KEY,       -- UUID
    created_at  DATETIME,
    title       TEXT                    -- auto-generated from first message
);

CREATE TABLE messages (
    id                      INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    session_id              TEXT REFERENCES chat_sessions(id),
    role                    TEXT,       -- "user" | "assistant"
    content                 TEXT,
    model_used              TEXT,       -- which Groq model responded
    layer_used              INTEGER,    -- 1, 2, or 3
    timestamp               DATETIME,
    hsoc_context_snapshot   TEXT        -- JSON snapshot of DB state at query time
);
```

The `hsoc_context_snapshot` field stores exactly what infrastructure data the AI saw when generating its response — useful for auditing AI decisions after an incident.

